    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept car in mint condition and the kind of example that is getting harder to find. It shows beautifully inside and out, runs and drives exactly as it should, and reflects careful ownership and maintenance. The interior is very clean, the exterior presents extremely well, and everything about it feels like a top-tier, properly cared-for vehicle. If you want a standout car that is ready to enjoy right away, this is an honest, high-quality example.",
