    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to be put to work, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a practical buyer who values affordability over perfection, but it still delivers solid everyday utility and a lot of value for the money. A smart opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive transportation, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and could be a great budget commuter, work car, or weekend project for someone handy. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is and could be a smart buy if you want something inexpensive without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic and want honest value, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5400.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget commuter with a tough-running drivetrain and plenty of usable life for the next owner. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed on the road. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs TLC, but the core mechanical package is there, making this a great candidate for someone who wants dependable transportation or a hands-on refresh without spending big money. Priced to move and worth a look if you appreciate good bones and straightforward mechanicals.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence you notice before you even turn the key\u2014a seasoned, honest machine with stories in its steel and plenty of road left for the right next owner. It\u2019s the sort of find that speaks to someone who sees possibility: a practical runabout, a rewarding project, or an affordable set of wheels with real personality. If you appreciate character over polish and want something memorable at an approachable entry point, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation value for the buyer who wants an affordable entry point. A practical choice for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone seeking a low-cost project, it delivers solid potential at a compelling price. If you're looking for inexpensive ownership with room to make it your own, this is a smart opportunity.",
